author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Keppel-KBS US REIT Says For Period Of 9 Nov 2017 To 31 March 2018 Net Property Income Was $22.328 Mln
text:
April 17 (Reuters) - Keppel-KBS US REIT:
* FOR PERIOD OF 9 NOV 2017 TO 31 MARCH 2018 NET PROPERTY INCOME WAS $22.328 MILLION
* FOR PERIOD OF 9 NOVEMBER 2017 TO 31 MARCH DPU WAS 2.32 US CENTS
* FOR PERIOD OF 9 NOV 2017 TO 31 MARCH 2018 GROSS REVENUE AMOUNTED TO $36.1 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
